      "source": "iupac_p34",
      "rule": "P-34.1.1.4 / P-15.1.8.2.2 retain 'anisole' as the PIN for bare CH3-O-C6H5 (methoxybenzene). Substituted anisoles fall back to the systematic methoxybenzene/{...} form; this entry is a whole-molecule retained-name match."
